Purchases of Equity Securities by the Issuer
On 15 September 2011, the Board of Directors authorized the repurchase of up to $1.0 billion of our outstanding
common stock. This program does not have a stated expiration date. We repurchase shares pursuant to Rules 10b5-1
and 10b-18 under the Exchange Act through repurchase agreements established with one or more brokers. There were
no purchases of stock during fiscal year 2021. At 30 September 2021, $485.3 million in share repurchase authorization
remained. Additional purchases will be completed at our discretion while maintaining sufficient funds for investing in our
business and pursuing growth opportunities.
