recorded in the second quarter to increase our existing liability for retained environmental obligations associated with
the sale of our former Amines business in September 2006. Refer to the Pace discussion within Note 16, Commitments
and Contingencies, for additional information. The loss did not have an impact on our cash flows for the fiscal year
ended 30 September 2020.
