Jazan Gas Project Company
On 19 April 2015, Jazan Gas Project Company, a joint venture between Air Products and ACWA Holding, entered into a
20-year oxygen and nitrogen supply agreement to supply Aramco’s oil refinery and power plant being built in Jazan,
